title.narrative: Technical Health Advisory and Administartion Management- Health Pooled Fund III

description.narrative: This activity ( Technical Health Advisory and Administartion Management- Health Pooled Fund III) is a component of South Sudan Health Pooled Fund Phase III reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £1,137,417. This component benefits South Sudan, and works in the following sector(s): Health education, Reproductive health care, Basic health care, Malaria control. , with the following implementing partners: Palladium International Ltd (UK). The start date is 25-10-2018 and the end date is 30-09-2023.
